You will likely need two conda environments to get this entire project working:

First, an environment for running the segment-anything toolset and the scheduling pipeline:

    # (this section is a work in progress)
    conda create --name segment-anything python=3.12
    conda install -c conda-forge segment-anything

To create a conda environment capable of cutie inference:
    conda create --name cutie python=3.10
    conda activate cutie
    pip install torch torchvision --index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/cu124
    git clone https://github.com/hkchengrex/Cutie
    cd Cutie
    pip install .
    python -m cutie.utils.download_models
    conda install ffmpeg
